            <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" Width="295" FontSize="20">
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="LeatherFace with his name unknown and being a massive lumber character he may not be the most iconic on the list but is definitely one of the most intimating with no motivation but pure influence by his family and the taste for murder and flesh. LeatherFace just chases his victims taking his signature chainsaw cutting up bodies and terrify people. He was a baby found in a bin badly disfigured and found by an old couple who themselves were unstable and always wanted a son. Soon as LeatherFace grew to the lumber giant he was and his family revealed their taste for human flesh it seems anyone that would cross paths with them were doomed"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="LeatherFace's appearance can vary but usually similar:"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="Age: between 20s and 30s"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="Height:  above 6ft"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="Build: Heavy/strong"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="Other defining characteristics:"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="Mute, badly disfigured face, wears a bag to cover face, very lumbering and strong"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
            		<Run Text="List of movies:"/>
            	</Span>
            	<LineBreak/>
            	<Span>
